title: GTA Mysterious Mod (2011-2015)
description:
So I finally decided to share my mod for GTA : San Andreas with everyone :)

I might still update it so don't get scared if you've saved it in bookmarks and it's gone. Just search for mod again ;)

INSTALLATION :
1. Unzip file anywhere you want.
2. Read the "READ ME OR YOU WON'T HAVE SOUND.txt" file in the mod's directory.
3. Enjoy the game :P

Since I can't post links here, search "GTA Mysterious Mod" in youtube and you'll see two videos from the very early stages of development from around 2 years ago. Some things are gone, new ones are added, so don't expect everything from videos to be in-game. I might make newer videos but to be honest I'm too lazy at the moment :D
If someone makes videos about all things in the mod, please share a comment with the link here so everyone can check them out X)
